title: Juventus 0-3 Milan | Statement win for Milan! | Serie A TIM
author: Serie A
description:
Milan got a very important victory that sends Juventus to Europa League places. Pioli's team has played a very good match that now puts them in the champions league places. Goals from Brahim Diaz, Ante Rebíc and Fikayo Tomori | Serie A TIM
